Hard constraints

- Do NOT weaken strict extraction semantics.
- Do NOT introduce speculative reconstruction.
- Do NOT guess filenames, offsets, or ordering.
- Do NOT silently change default archive behavior.
- Keep this packet experimental and bounded.
- Deterministic behavior is required.
- Recovery may only use verified data and verified local headers.

